            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Miami Beach Police say the officer was responding to an emergency call on the department’s ATV. The Corvette didn’t yield at an intersection, which is what lead to the collision. It turns out the guy driving that red convertible sports car, Nash Martin, has a ",
