          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Fortunately, the officer’s injuries weren’t too serious. He was treated and released from the hospital. That’s especially fortunate for Martin, because if the officer were seriously hurt he would be facing even stiffer consequences for the wreck.",
